Run the following commands on the command line in order:

cd ~
git clone --recursive https://github.com/mihirgogate/dotfiles.git dotfiles
chmod +x dotfiles/setup.sh
./dotfiles/setup.sh


# Tools to install to use the dotfiles
- git (https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Getting-Started-Installing-Git)
- tmux (https://linuxize.com/post/getting-started-with-tmux/)
- zsh shell (https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Installing-ZSH)
- vim 8+ (https://www.vim.org/git.php)
